https://screencast-o-matic.com/

This is the link on a software that can be used to make video recordings of the screen. I am used to 

https://obsproject.com/

but the one mentioned in the first line also supports the feature of highligting the mouse taps. That simplifies the job because OBS would require installation of external software for that.
Not to forget the name that I always forget,

https://handbrake.fr/

Handbrake is the one I use to edit the videos I get. Don't forget to remove the background music where it is not needed not to scare the devs away!
